                    <TextBlock
                        Margin="80,0,80,10"
                        HorizontalAlignment="Center"
                        VerticalAlignment="Top"
                        FontFamily="{ThemeResource Light}"
                        FontSize="18"
                        Opacity="0.7"
                        TextAlignment="Center"
                        TextWrapping="Wrap">
                        Fancy an elevated hotel experience? Our superior 42 square meters deluxe room features elegant traditional Filipino interiors that creates a sensation of timeless comfort. Enjoy a great night’s sleep and snuggle in our king-sized bed and in-house amenities.
